@@$TJvScrollBox
<TITLE TJvScrollBox overview>
<GROUP JVCL.Miscel>
  TJvScrollBox is a scroll box that supports extended features such as hot tracking. 
  
  You can use OnMouseEnter and OnMouseLeave to alter the controls look or behavoir, when the user 
  moves the mouse pointer over the control.
  
  Alternatively, you can use property HotTrack to highlight the scroll box automatically when the
  mouse passes over it.

  Use OnHorizontalScroll and OnVerticalScroll to take action when the user scrolls the specified
  scroll bar.
  
  Property HintColor can be used to set a different color of the Help hint boxes for the scroll box.
