@@TJvScrollBox
<GROUP TJvScrollBox>
Summary
  Supports extended features such as hot tracking.
Description
  Use property HotTrack to highlight the scroll box when mouse passes over it. Use property HintColor 
  to change the color of the hint boxes for the scroll box.
  
  You can use the events OnHorizontalScroll, OnVerticalScroll to be notified when the user scrolls the
  bars belonging to the scroll box.  
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvScrollBox.Create
Summary
  Creates and initializes a new TJvScrollBox object.
Description
  Use Create to create and initialize a new TJvScrollBox object.
  
  Create calls the inherited Create method, then sets the initial values for the scroll box as follows: 

  * HintColor is set to clInfoBk.
  * HotTrack is set to False.
  * csAcceptsControls is added to ControlStyle.  
Parameters
  AOwner - A component, typically the form, that is responsible for freeing the scroll box.
