@@TJvScrollBox.CMCtl3DChanged
Summary
  Responds when the Ctrl3D property changes.
Description
  CMCtl3DChanged is called automatically when the Ctl3D property changes. It triggers the 
  OnCtl3DChanged event.
Parameters
  Msg - Represents the parameters of the Windows message that informs the scroll box of the Ctl3D 
        change.
See Also
  OnCtl3DChanged
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvScrollBox.CMMouseEnter
Summary
  Responds when the mouse pointer moves over the scroll box.
Description
  CMMouseEnter is called automatically when the mouse pointer moves over the scroll box. It sets the
  hint color for the application to the property specified by HintColor, sets the Ctl3D property
  to true if property HotTrack is true, and triggers the OnMouseEnter event.
Parameters
  Msg - Represents the parameters of the Windows message that informs the scroll box of the event.
See Also
  CMMouseLeave, OnMouseEnter, OnMouseLeave
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvScrollBox.CMMouseLeave
Summary
  Responds when the mouse pointer moves off the scroll box.
Description
  CMMouseEnter is called automatically when the mouse pointer moves off the scroll box. It resets the
  hint color for the application, sets the Ctl3D property to false if property HotTrack is true, and
  triggers the OnMouseLeave event.
Parameters
  Msg - Represents the parameters of the Windows message that informs the scroll box of the event.
See Also
  CMMouseEnter, OnMouseEnter, OnMouseLeave
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvScrollBox.CMParentColorChanged
Summary
  Responds when the color of the parent of the scroll box changes.
Description
  CMParentColorChanged is called automatically when the color of the parent of the scroll box changes.
  It triggers the OnParentColorChange event.
Parameters
  Msg - Represents the parameters of the Windows message that informs the scroll box of the parent
        color change.
See Also
  OnParentColorChange
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvScrollBox.HintColor
Summary
  Determines the color of the hint boxes for the Help Hints for the scroll box.
Description
  Use HintColor to specify the hint box color. A default color value of clInfoBk is set for the
  HintColor property in the constructor when the application is created. To change the HintColor
  assign it a new TColor value.
See Also
  HotTrack
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvScrollBox.HotTrack
Summary
  Specifies whether the scroll box is highlighted when the mouse passes over it.
Description
  Set HotTrack to True to provide visual feedback about which item is under the mouse. When HotTrack
  is True. When HotTrack is False, there is no visual feedback when the mouse passes over this control.
See Also 
  OnMouseEnter, OnMouseLeave
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvScrollBox.OnCtl3DChanged
Summary
